e higher with spec. lvl so that we can use our low level styles and actually have them do more damage than a non-styled attack?  I really do think it SHOULD be based on spec. level too, I know just with the Twin Spikes example I used if it scaled with char. level you'd have any Infy with 2 pts in DW having a nice anytime style all of a sudden, and I'm sure there's plenty of other examples with other classes. <p>Nirala HammahMastah<br>
&lt;The Kindred&gt;<br>
